  "texts": [
    "This approach included the functionality to track lesions across time points and consider new lesions.",
    "This tracking is necessary for longitudinal volume and progression monitoring based on individual lesions.",
    "Oermann et al.",
    "developed an architecture that can segment brain metastases using longitudinal imaging data 28.",
    "The architecture, which they call \"segmentation through time\", uses a collection of U-Nets."
  ],
